<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DSVerify</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #5865F2;
            --primary-dark: #4752c4;
            --secondary: #57F287;
            --dark: #1e1f29;
            --darker: #171820;
            --light: #f0f0f0;
            --text: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #b9bbbe;
            --card-bg: rgba(30, 31, 41, 0.8);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        
        .home-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .brand-logo {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        
        .description {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .description:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary), var(--primary));
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 22px;
            animation: borderAnimation 3s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        
        .verify-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            padding: 1.3rem 3rem;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            margin-top: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.3);
        }
        
        .verify-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="home-container">
        <div class="brand-logo">DSVerify</div>
        
        <p class="tagline">
            Premium Verification System
        </p>
        
        <div class="description">
            DSVerify is a custom-built, high-performance verification bot developed by @fmtg. 
            Designed for exclusive communities, it provides seamless and secure authentication 
            with advanced features tailored for premium user management. The system offers 
            enterprise-grade reliability with a focus on privacy and efficiency, ensuring 
            a smooth experience for both administrators and community members.
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
            <span>Custom built with Discord.js & Node.js</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>